Determine length of TidyTuesday Data

ttd_length.Rd

Determine length of TidyTuesday Data

Usage

ttd_length(ttd)

Arguments

ttd

A list of data frames from load_tt_data()

Value

integer length of ttd

Examples

ttd <- load_tt_data("Moore’s Law")
